By: Sri Sankarâchârya
---
Having a firm grasp of this secret Knowledge (that the Self is Brahman), the
Supreme Goal, and being free from defects and vanity people should always
fix their minds on Brahman which is always the same. For no man who knows
Brahman to be different from himself is a knower of Truth.
